citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:10pm on 03-JUL-
23.
Inspector attempted to reach licensee by all possible means, honking car horn, knocking on car door and waiting for 40
minutes.
End Section
